libbc-concurrency (1.0.1-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Fix data race (tsan) on worker slot reads via foreach_slot.
    After dispatch_and_wait, foreach_slot now re-acquires work_done
    on each worker before reading its slot, ensuring tsan-visible
    happens-before for callers that read worker-produced pointers
    or buffers (e.g. bc-hash error_collector flush).

 -- Younes Benmoussa <younes.benmoussa@pm.me>  Sun, 19 Apr 2026 14:00:00 +0000

libbc-concurrency (1.0.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial public release.
  * Worker pool: MPMC queue-backed, configurable worker count,
    per-slot lifetime callbacks.
  * Typed dispatch and shared cross-worker context.
  * Signal-safe shutdown coordination.
  * Full sanitizer coverage (asan / tsan / ubsan / memcheck) and
    cppcheck-clean sources.

 -- Younes Benmoussa <younes.benmoussa@pm.me>  Sun, 19 Apr 2026 12:00:00 +0000
